Install on your local computer for development:
-----------------------------------------------

Requirements:
  * Ruby 2.1
  * Rubygem 2.2.2
  * Bundler 1.6.2
  * MongoDB 2.6.4

  * Open one terminal and run:
  $ ./mongo.sh
  # Wait until it says:
    ...  
  2014-10-03T21:12:22.990+0200 [initandlisten] waiting for connections on port 27017

  * Open another terminal and run:
  $ bundle install
  $ bundle exec cucumber
  # if everything is green, run:
  $ bundle exec ruby backend.rb

